description:
Andrew was a fire fighter for a few years before he decided it was time for a career change.
"It was fun, but really stressful," he said. "Long hours, and dangerous too."
So now he's training to be a police officer. I didn't think there would be much of a difference there, but he seemed excited about it.
Andrew is 22, single, and he lives on the east coast.
He hits the gym hard every day. His motivation: impressing the ladies, of course.
"I used to be skinny," he said. "The girls didn't respond to that as much as they do now. They love the muscles."
His big dick probably doesn't hurt either!
title: Andrew
